Place your door games here.
Create links for dosemu

ln -s /opt/photonbbs/doors /opt/photonbbs/.dosemu/drive_c/doors
ln -sf /dev/shm/photonbbs/doors/nodes /opt/photonbbs/.dosemu/drive_c/nodeinfo

** Lunatix will not work over a link, place luna in /opt/photonbbs/.dosemu/drive_c

---
To access door games from within the teleconference, type /DOORS or /MENU.
This will display a list of available external commands and door games, filtered by your security level.
Each entry shows the command to type and a description. Just type the command (e.g. /1, /2, etc) to launch the door.
